CLOTHING/
SUIT SEPARATES/
Suits/




Suits

About Suits

Men's Suits: Tailored Slim Fit Suits, Skinny & Classic Fit Suits
Just like every man’s suit doesn’t fit each person the same, particular men’s suits are specific to certain situations. Going for something casual but sophisticated? Trying to impress that boss of yours? Or that girl you’re going on a date with? Don’t worry, Perry Ellis has a three-piece suit that tailors to you and your setting. With every guy in mind, we put our distinctive designs — like herringbone, sharkskin, chambray and iridescent — into sizes that range from very slim fit to big & tall. And of course, regular fit for the not-so-regular man. Shopping for business, or for pleasure? Whether you call them pants, slacks or trousers, jackets, sport coats or blazers, we bring you the perfect pairing finished with a tailored fit.
For the traveling businessman, or just a guy who stays on the go, our non-iron, wrinkle-free Travel Luxe suit collection is perfect for you — and these washable suits are certified for every professional. Need wedding wear? Linen suits are lightweight, breathable and perfect to exchange beach nuptials in. Whether you’re the groom, best man or a groomsmen, suit up in style because those pictures really do last a lifetime. And you don’t want to be the one who goes underdressed to any formal affair. That statement holds true for prom, homecoming, graduation or a black-tie event. Solid, slightly striped, heathered? Play it fashion forward in your black, navy blue, gray or white suit when you add a sleek dress shirt, tie and pocket square for that extra pop of color. Guys in suits always tend to look better and feel better, so grab a suit be the best version of you.















