CLOTHING/
PANTS/
Dress Pants/




Dress Pants

About Dress Pants

Men's Dress Pants and Slacks: Slim Fit, Very Slim Fit & Classic Fit
No matter what the occasion or style of pant, we know the importance of finding that perfect-fitting pair. Something sleek, classy and dapper that you’ve been searching far and wide for. With four different fits — slim, regular, classic and modern — in each of various-styled slacks, every guy can find the style they strive for in the size that fits. After all, different guys like different styles, and dress pants can be the difference maker to any outfit. Keep it casual but classy when you pick up a pair of chinos, which give a perfect professional look while keeping a laid-back approach. They show that you’re trendy, but don’t take fashion too serious. Have an old-school business style with a modern touch? Then Perry Ellis Portfolio pleated or double-pleated pants are the exact trouser you’re looking for. Incorporating a non-iron, wrinkle-free finish into a style that’s never out of season, you can pay homage to the timeless looks of yesteryear while impressing everyone at the office. Skip the dry cleaner, because our trousers are machine washable, which means they’re an excellent wardrobe addition for the on-the-go businessman.
Headed to prom, homecoming, formal or just a black-tie event? Arrive in style when you pair your pants with suit separates to make a three-piece suit that’s sure to make you shine. Add a tie and pocket square to include a pop of color into your wardrobe. Or just go for the minimalist look in the office or on the weekend when you pair your dress pants with a polo or knit. With fabrications like sharkskin, herringbone, heather, chambray, melange, bengaline and linen in slim fit to big & tall, you’re assured to find the style you’re looking for in the fit you deserve.















