Product Coordinator at Perry Ellis International Inc. • JOFDAV
























This job listing has expired and the position may no longer be open for hire.






    Product Coordinator
      at Perry Ellis International Inc.
  

    Posted in Art about 1 month ago.
  

      This job brought to you by eQuest


Type: Full-Time
Location: New York, New York
  
Job Description:

PERRY ELLIS INTERNATIONAL
 Product Coordinator – PERRY ELLIS Accessories (Belts/SLG)
  
 DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES: 
  Send/Receive packages, sketches and specs out for development 
  Create Spec Sheets 
  Organize raw material library 
  Maintain and update files 
  Communicate with factories 
  Update and initial analysis of excel spreadsheet 
  Maintain info on PAC share drives 
  Sample requests / initial costs 
  Approve samples based on specs 
  Data entry     
 SKILLS, KNOWLEDGE AND ABILITIES:
  Strong Communication skills 
  Detail orientated 
  Independently worker   
  Flexible hours 
  Functions well in ambiguous situations     
  Multi task with multiple deadlines 
  Microsoft office , Photoshop, Illustrator 
  Fashion/Design aptitude 
  Organized   
 MINIMUM REQUIREMENTS: 
  1 – 2 years experience working in product development  
  Drawing, Photoshop and/or Illustrator a major plus  
