About Us
Dear Valued Customer:
Appearances and first impressions in the corporate world are vital. At Perry Ellis International (PEI),
           a leader in apparel manufacturing, we understand that looking your best is a component of being your best.
           Your company deserves high-quality products to match your business standards. PEI’s Corporate Sales Division is proud
           to offer an ever-expanding collection of Callaway® apparel to give your company a polished, professional appearance.
Callaway, a dominant force in golf apparel, is known for its superior performance-driven construction. The most powerful
             brand name in the sport, Callaway apparel products are created with both pro athletes and sophisticated corporate customers
             in mind. Innovative, technological and constructed with the finest functional features, Callaway offers authentic style to match
             your company’s vision and purpose. As a powerhouse retailer, our core competency lies in superior apparel manufacturing you can trust.
             Our team of worldwide professionals is always available to fulfill your needs.
In the early part of 2014, we expanded our embroidery capabilities by acquiring additional state-of-the-art embroidery machines and moving 
            production into a spacious Tampa facility, enabling us to deliver even quicker lead times.We offer a comprehensive product assortment to the
             corporate market. From performance polo shirts to pullovers, outerwear and embroidery, we provide a one-stop shopping experience. Easy. 
            Efficient. Excellent.
You want your company to be the best, let us help you look the part.
To place an order, request a catalog or for any inquiries, please contact us.
B2B LOGIN



About Perry Ellis International, Inc















Our MISSION:
Callaway offers classic, authentic and premium apparel for those who love the game and want to perform their best on and off the course with the latest in design and technology innovation.







