Embroidery






PEI’s state-of-the-art embroidery center
                        allows us to execute jobs quickly, as well as
                        with unparalleled precision and quality.
                        We have SWF embroidery machines that
                        can sew 1,000 stitches per minute and have
                        enough memory to hold 100 designs.
                        So if you’re in the market for fast, hassle-free
                        embroidery work, PEI has you covered.
 

 Perry Ellis International’s new embroidery
                        technology includes software capable of memorizing
                        scores of designs, facilitating fast, high-quality turnarounds.
 In-house embroidery service includes a retail fold
                         in a custom-made poly bag and Callaway embellished tissue paper.









CONTACT US

Our Callaway® apparel brand is sold exclusively through promotional product distributors. 
If you are a new distributor, please contact us to open an account. For corporate buyers or individual customers,
          we would be happy to refer you to a local Callaway apparel distributor, 
         so you too can enjoy this season’s great styles and colors. 
            You want your company to be the best, let us help you look the part.
Look forward to hearing from you!




Contact us and we'll get back to you within 24 hours.
